data.description: Marvelous home in Bullard ISD with 2.489 acres already fenced in with 3 bedrooms, 3 bath and 5 garages. There is an additional room that could serve as your office or fourth bedroom but has not closet. The home has 3000 square feet allows plenty of room to entertain. Amazing ceiling treatments throughout, vaulted ceilings w/cedar beams and double recessed with crown molding, custom cabinetry, and fireplace!  The kitchen is equipped with a large island, desk area, gas cooktop, granite countertops, new stainless appliances, and oversized breakfast area! Formal dining, complete with custom barn doors, can be used as an office area, playroom, etc.!  The sunroom has large glass doors that allows you to look into the backyard and serves as an optional flex space! A generous master suite offers a walk-in closet, wonderful bath, and privacy. Also, two guest rooms with two baths nearby, one being a Rebath. The oversized utility room has a sink accompanied with plentiful storage. The covered patio has an extended area with a built-in grill to enjoy the country living!  The property has 3 detached garages with epoxy floors (heated and cooled) is additional square footage away from the home. The options are limitless, could easily be converted to a mother-in-law area. Not to forget, the RV storage has electricity.  Come See! Come Buy!
